    <briefdescription>
<para>Per-body simulation state buffers for free rigid-body stepping. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Stores pose, velocity, and accumulated wrench terms for each body. Linear quantities are in world coordinates (m, m/s, N), angular quantities are in world coordinates (rad/s, N*m). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
